{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-product","blocks":{"title_fNd8xH":{"type":"title","settings":{}},"text_HWx4XN":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<strong>Hoodie Blanket<\/strong>","text_style":"subtitle"}},"text_EFDcjF":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<em>Zōk gave me relief within minutes—no more relying on painkillers!  It’s small, simple to use, and has become my go-to for headache relief. <\/em><em><strong>Zara A<\/strong><\/em>","text_style":"body"}},"price_dr9ifw":{"type":"price","settings":{}},"buy_buttons":{"type":"buy_buttons","settings":{"shipping-txt":"<strong>2~4 Day Shipping from Dhaka, Bangladesh<\/strong>🇧🇩","show_dynamic_checkout":false,"show_gift_card_recipient":true}},"a134f827-c44e-4834-abbb-dea857d93816":{"type":"icon-with-text","settings":{"layout":"horizontal","icon_1":"truck","heading_1":"Shipped from Dhaka","icon_2":"return","heading_2":"Money Back Gurantee","icon_3":"price_tag","heading_3":"Cash on Delivery"}},"137bee7a-dd9c-415e-ac1c-7c29ab2fd653":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Shipping","icon":"truck","content":"<p>We are based in Dubai however we have a warehouse in Dhaka, hence shipments all over<strong> Bangladesh take only 2-4 days and cost 100 Taka. <\/strong><\/p>","page":""}},"55879359-71f2-45bb-9e58-3c0de78c7375":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Return & Refund Policy","icon":"return","content":"<p><strong>1.1 Return Due To Change Of Mind<\/strong><\/p><p>We will happily accept returns due to change of mind as long as a request to return is received by us within 72 hours of receipt of item. <\/p><p>Once approved, refunds will be processed to their original payment method. We will notify you once this has been completed through email.<\/p><p>We will refund the value of the goods returned but will NOT refund the value of any shipping paid.<\/p><p><strong>1.2 Cancellations<\/strong><\/p><p>If you change your mind before a tracking numbers has been generated, we are able to accept c